languages.text: "How many more of you mutineers are hiding on my ship? I want to know your names, I want to know where you meet — everything."

languages.text: «¿Cuántos amotinados más hay en la nave? Me va a decir sus nombres y dónde se congregan: lo quiero saber todo».
languages.original_text: "How many more of you mutineers are hiding on my ship? I want to know your names, I want to know where you meet — everything."

traits.locale_text: «¿Cuántos amotinados más hay en la nave? Me va a decir sus nombres y dónde se congregan: lo quiero saber todo».

languages.text: 「あとどれほどの反逆者たち我が船にが潜んでいるんだ？名前に密会場所…洗いざらい教えろ」
languages.original_text: "How many more of you mutineers are hiding on my ship? I want to know your names, I want to know where you meet — everything."

traits.locale_text: 「あとどれほどの反逆者たち我が船にが潜んでいるんだ？名前に密会場所…洗いざらい教えろ」

languages.text: “这艘船上还有多少叛乱分子？告诉我他们的名字，还有他们见面的地点，我要知道所有的一切。”
languages.original_text: "How many more of you mutineers are hiding on my ship? I want to know your names, I want to know where you meet — everything."

traits.locale_text: “这艘船上还有多少叛乱分子？告诉我他们的名字，还有他们见面的地点，我要知道所有的一切。”

languages.text: "Wie viele von euch Meuterern verstecken sich auf meinem Schiff? Ich will eure Namen, ich will wissen, wo ihr euch trefft ... alles."
languages.original_text: "How many more of you mutineers are hiding on my ship? I want to know your names, I want to know where you meet — everything."

traits.locale_text: "Wie viele von euch Meuterern verstecken sich auf meinem Schiff? Ich will eure Namen, ich will wissen, wo ihr euch trefft ... alles."

languages.text: « Combien d'autres mutins de votre acabit se cachent encore à bord de mon vaisseau ? Vous allez me divulguer leurs noms, l'endroit où ils se réunissent, tout. »
languages.original_text: "How many more of you mutineers are hiding on my ship? I want to know your names, I want to know where you meet — everything."

languages.text: "Siz isyancılardan gemimde kaç tane var? İsimlerinizi bilmek istiyorum. Nerede buluştuğunuzu, her şeyi bilmek istiyorum."
languages.original_text: "How many more of you mutineers are hiding on my ship? I want to know your names, I want to know where you meet — everything."
